column8: Cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of rain. The chance of a thunderstorm. Light winds becoming east to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h in the evening.

Cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of showers in the morning and early afternoon. The chance of a thunderstorm in the morning and early afternoon. Winds north to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h tending northwest to southwesterly before dawn then tending southwesterly in the morning.
Partly cloudy. Winds southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h becoming light before dawn then becoming south to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h in the morning.
Partly cloudy. Medium (40%) chance of showers, most likely later in the day. Winds easterly 15 to 20 km/h shifting west to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h during the day.
Medium (40%) chance of showers, most likely during the morning. Mostly sunny afternoon. Light winds becoming southwesterly 20 to 25 km/h during the morning.
